        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Answer: C \u2014 Jury service is limited to U.S. citizens."
        },
        {
          "type": "h3",
          "text": "Civics Q10 \u2014 In presidential elections, who casts the decisive votes?"
        },
        {
          "type": "ol",
          "items": [
            "A) The national popular vote",
            "B) The Supreme Court",
            "C) The Electoral College",
            "D) The House of Representatives in every election"
